@DATABASE "Park Patrol"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - P - Park Patrol"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - P
                   ====================================

                                Park Patrol
                                ===========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(53949,0)"}          53949,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(53188,255)"}          53188,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Energy*100 = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(53200,128)"}          53200,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         "Energy*100" means that the number you POKE will
                         be multiplied by 100.


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
